            <div class="tool-rank">01</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">theStacc <span class="winner-badge">★ Editor's Pick</span></div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for publish-ready output · End-to-end pipeline</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$99<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Content SEO module</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>30 publish-ready articles a month — written, scored, shipped</li>
                <li>URL-trained brand voice (no manual setup)</li>
                <li>Direct publishing to WordPress, Ghost, Webflow, Shopify</li>
                <li>Internal linking and schema added automatically</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Long-form focus — no social caption templates</li>
                <li>No per-draft purchase — monthly subscription only</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> SMBs and bloggers who want articles published, not just drafted.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start $1 trial →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">02</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Jasper</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best AI blog writer for marketing teams</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$59<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Creator plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Best-in-class brand voice + knowledge base</li>
                <li>50+ team workflow features (review, approvals)</li>
