            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Marketing teams that need brand voice + approvals.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/jasper-ai/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read Jasper review →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">03</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Koala AI</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best budget AI blog writer</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$25<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Essential plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Solid drafts at the cheapest credible price</li>
